    About this hotel

    Located in central Sacramento, this simple hotel is a block from Governor’s Mansion State Historic Park, 6 blocks from the Sacramento Convention Center and 1.7 miles from Crocker Art Museum. …

    The straightforward rooms all feature breakfast tables and coffeemakers, as well as cable TV and free WiFi. Some include minifridges, and suites come with separate sitting areas.

    Continental breakfast is free, and the hotel has a newsstand.

    Check-out time: 11:00 AM
